product_specification.Warranty Summary: Brand Warranty of 1 Year Available for Mobile and 6 Months for Accessories

product_description.Design: This elegant looking smartphone features a high-quality screen and a 3D Flowing Blaze design. So, not only does it let you enjoy your movies, videos, and more in stunning visuals, but it also ensures that you get to flaunt its stylish design too. It even features a Blue Light Sheild, which exudes the harmful blue light from the screen and thereby keeps you away from experiencing eye strain. So, you can use it day and night without eye fatigue.
product_description.Unlock It Easily: It has a rear Fingerprint Sensor and an AI Face Unlock feature. By using these features, you can unlock the device by glancing at it or by simply pressing the Sensor. Its high-quality facial recognition capability allows it to recognise you via the 128 biometric points easily. So, you can bid farewell to the strenuous task of remembering many passwords and codes.
